summary: A custom body replacer specifically tweaked to emphasis wider shoulder, bigger breast and full thigh to create what you call a sexy amazonian woman while not being overly muscular.
descriptionHtml:
[center][IMG]http://i.imgur.com/ORGLXcV.png[/IMG][/center]
[heading][center][i][size=5][color=#7d6f53]A custom body replacer specifically tweaked to emphasis wider shoulder, bigger breast and full thigh to create what you call a sexy amazonian woman while not being overly muscular.[/color][/size][/i][/center][/heading]
[center][IMG]http://i.imgur.com/8wgyfsI.png[/IMG][/center]

[heading][size=5][color=#7d6f53][b][i]SeveNBase Options:[/i][/b][/color][/size][/heading]
[size=2][color=#7d6f53][b]Original :[/b][/color]
Based on SeveNBase 1st edition by Sevennity with a tweaked full soft breast and wider shoulder, supports BBP.

[color=#7d6f53][b]Natural :[/b][/color]
Based on SeveNBase 1st edition by Sevennity with a tweaked full soft gravity oriented breast and wider shoulder, supports BBP.

[color=#7d6f53][b]Cleavage :[/b][/color]
Based on SeveNBase 1st edition by Sevennity with a tweaked cleavage push up effect breast (for MODDERS who want to show off upper parts of the breast aka cleavage) and wider shoulder, supports BBP.

[color=#7d6f53][b]TBBP :[/b][/color]
Based on SeveNBase 1st edition by Sevennity, supports TBBP.

[color=#7d6f53][b]Bombshell :[/b][/color]
Sevennity's new body SeveNBase3 Bombshell v3.2 with more defined calves and slender knees, supports BBP. There are three versions: Nude Standard,Nude bounce+ and Bikini.

[color=#7d6f53][b]Bombshell B-CUP:[/b][/color]
Sevennity's SeveNBase3 Bombshell v3.3 body, a B-CUP version of the Bombshell body.

[color=#7d6f53][b]Non BBP versions of Original and Cleavage:[/b][/color]
Same shape as Original and Cleavage, without BBP by FastestDog, if you want to use it with BBP armors you still need a compatible skeleton.

Check the IMAGE TAB for comparison screenshots(Natural/Original/TBBP/Bombshell).
Every package contains animation files(by LeCid), they are required to make sure that the breast movement works properly. If you don't like them, you can also try [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/13272/?]Victorias High Heel walk Animation plus BBP[/url] by XP32.[/size]

[heading][size=5][color=#844747][i]SeveNBase Requirements:[/i][/color][/size][/heading]
[size=2]To run the Mod properly you have to install a skeleton which supports BBP or TBBP such as XP32's [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/26800/?]XP32 Maximum Skeleton[/url] (BBP and TBBP support) OR one of Skulltyrant's [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/16712/?]Custom Skeleton Replacers[/url] (BBP or TBBP if you use the TBBP body), if not you'll get a [color=red][b]crash[/b][/color] at startup. Be sure you have the SeveNBase package of your choice already installed before installing the skeleton.

The bodies work with every UNP compatible skin textures but they are not included so you will need UNP skin textures such as [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/35267/?]SG textures[/url] by Hellosanta or [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/24318/?]Barbarian and Milkdrinker Skin[/url] by HoneyVanity.
ADDITIONAL you can use modified FitnessBody normal maps by SvarogNL, SGTexturesRenewal 7B normal maps by Hellosanta or Barbarian and Milkdrinker Skin normal maps by HoneyVanity (you can find them under OPTIONAL FILES), which are patched with Sevennity's breast patch. Read the text files in the archive!
[/size]

[heading][size=5][color=#7d6f53][i]SeveNBase Installation(READ THIS CAREFULLY!!):[/i][/color][/size][/heading]
[size=2]Step 1:
If you haven't already installed an UNP skin texture set, do this now.
Step 2:
Install the SeveNBase body of your choice(you can do this with the Modmanger or manually)
Step 3:
Install a compatible skeleton. BBP compatible for the Natural, the Original or the Bombshell body. TBBP compatible for the TBBP body(take a look at the FORUMS tab of this page, there is a list of Skulltyrant's TBBP skeletons). XP32's Maximum skeleton is BBP AND TBBP compatible.
OVERWRITE the files from the SeveNBase package.
Step 4:
If you are using FNIS you will have to run GenearatFNISforUsers.
Step 5:
Have fun![/size]

[heading][size=5][color=#7d6f53][i]SeveNBase Uninstall:[/i][/color][/size][/heading]
[size=2]Installed with ModManager: remove the mod with the ModManager
Manualy installed: remove the files which come with the archive manually[/size]

[heading][size=5][color=#844747][i]SeveNBase Attention:[/i][/color][/size][/heading]
[size=2]Back up your files! We are not responsible for any data loss!

[color=red][b]Patches[/b][/color]: Check the MISCELLANEOUS files for patches!
FemaleOrcFix: with this ESP female Orcs use female animations.
VanillaAnimationsPatch: if you don't like the animations which come with SeveNBase, apply this patch AFTER you have installed the body of your choice.[/size]

[heading][size=5][color=#7d6f53][i]SeveNBase Armors:[/i][/color][/size][/heading]
[size=2]Crosscrusade started to convert his [color=red][url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/34160/?]Sexy Vanilla Female Armor[/url][/color] mod. Check it out for updates!
Check out Sevennity's tumblr page for updates(armors/normal maps) for the [color=red][url=http://sevennity.tumblr.com/post/52008379972/sevenbase3-bombshell-female-body-replacer]Bombshell body[/url][/size][/color]!
Take a look at the FORUMS tab of this page for armor updates(topic: Armors/Clothing for SeveNBase)
